room_title: Escape room "Office of Secret Agent 22" by Hysterium Escapes in Fort Wayne
room_description:
You have 60 minutes to gather the appropriate information for the FBI to properly identify and locate Secret Agent 22. Upon entering his father's office, you find that a booby trap has triggered and you and your friends are locked in!
Solve the clues, find the flash drive, gather the information and diffuse the bomb before you are blown to smithereens!
